edu.umn.nlpengine

Interface Document

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Metadata, TextRange
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDocument

    public Document
extends TextRange, Metadata

    A text document and its associated label indices. Implements interface TextRange as the range of the document. Implements interface Metadata with the artifact metadata.

    See Also:
    interface TextRange, interface Metadata
